import math

def find_max_sub_rectangle(n, m, x, y, a, b):
    gcd = math.gcd(a, b)
    a //= gcd
    b //= gcd
    max_ratio = min(n // a, m // b)
    a /= max_ratio
    b *= max_ratio
    x1 = max(0, min(x - (a + 1) // 2, n - a))
    y1 = max(0, min(y - (b + 1) // 2, m - b))
    return (x1, y1, x1 + a, y1 + b)

    return (x1, y1, x1 + a, y1 + b)
